    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Nice chore work! Super weird that the actual size of the lib went up 11kb gz:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/123822/37174072-c49bc634-2315-11e8-88cc-28c2f93b161f.png)\r\n\r\nhttps://bundlesize-store.now.sh/build?info=%7B%22files%22%3A%5B%7B%22maxSize%22%3A102400%2C%22path%22%3A%22.%2Fdist%2Finstantsearch.min.js%22%2C%22size%22%3A109294%2C%22compression%22%3A%22gzip%22%2C%22master%22%3A97781%7D%5D%2C%22repo%22%3A%22algolia%2Finstantsearch.js%22%2C%22branch%22%3A%22misc%2Fmulti-package-updates%22%2C%22commit_message%22%3A%22Merge%20594e300dcfca7a4046f9c300249ee91cb686c966%20into%2079ebd66bda1b7ccc4f2d8a47ef67f2bb8c5b39c5%22%2C%22sha%22%3A%22594e300dcfca7a4046f9c300249ee91cb686c966%22%7D\r\n\r\nMaybe it's just because bundlesize itself was updated. Because I see no other lib that could be responsible for this in the updates.",
